Npcyell_9284_Text: Behold, the sword art of legend─Zanmato!
Npcyell_9285_Text: Thank your lucky stars Zanmato thirsts not for your blood!
Npcyell_9291_Text: Fortune favors the bold, and if you are truly worthy, your luck will hold!
Npcyell_9292_Text: Three cups I present! One contains riches, another my faithful hound! And the last...well, nothing at all!
Npcyell_9293_Text: Uncover the coin, and it is yours. Chance upon Daigoro, and you will be sent running with your tail between your legs!
Npcyell_9294_Text: Before I count to three, make your choice!
Npcyell_9298_Text: Well, well! The kami smile upon you, brave one!
Npcyell_9299_Text: If you are still game, so am I!
Npcyell_9309_Text: I fear our little game must soon come to an end. One last chance for Zanmato to shine!
Npcyell_9310_Text: Fleet of foot, and fortunate to boot! A well-deserved victory!
Npcyell_9428_Text: Foolish bamboo! You dare to face my blade!?
Npcyell_9429_Text: Let the bamboo fall where it may!
